<h1 class="Heading">Experience Bauchi at its best</h1>
<h3><em>Showing you the Nigeria you didn't think exists</em></h3>

<div class="down-box">

</div>


<h2>Why should you explore Bauchi?</h2>

<p>Bauchi is loacted in the Northern Region of Nigeria. With an average temperature of and rainfall of,<br>
   Bauchi seems to be the perfect place for your Nothern Nigeria Vacation.</p>
   <br>
   <h2>Sights to look forward to In Bauchi</h2>
   <ul>
     <li><strong>Yankari Games Reserve</strong></li>
    <p>Yankari Games Reserve is the major tourist attraction in Bauchi. Like other Games Reserve all over the world, <br>The games Reserve gives you access to animals and other beautiful sights. <br>Giving you a whole new Northern experience.</p>

     <img src="https://hometown.ng/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/dsc_0218e-580x387.jpg" alt="Yankari Games Reserve">
     <img src="https://sunnewsonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_9522-580x387.jpghttps://sunnewsonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_9522-580x387.jpghttps://sunnewsonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_9522-580x387.jpg" alt="">
<p></p>

     <li><strong>The Emir's Palace</strong></li>
     <p>If you love history like me, you'll understand how important it is to visit the Emir of Bauchi's palace.
       <br>From the gates of the palace, you get an insight of what the empire used to be before amalgamation.</p>
       <br>
       <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/00/Bauchi_Emirates_Palace.jpg" alt="Emir's Palace Bauchi">
<p></p>
     <li><strong>Rocky views and Water bodies</strong></li>
     <p>One of the beautiful things about Bauchi is the sight of rocks and water. It helps you relax.</p>
     <img src="https://i0.wp.com/kaynuli.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/explore_bauchi_7.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1" alt="Rocks and water view at Yankari Games Reserve" width="500">
<br>
<p></p>
     <li><strong>The Historical City Gates</strong></li>
     <p>The City Gates are nine in number and they tell us  the tales of how people protected themselves aginst predators in the 19th century.</p>
     <img src="https://sunnewsonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/HISTORIC-BAUCHI-GATE.jpg" alt="City Gates, Bauchi" width="500px">
<br>
<p></p>
    <li><strong>Food</strong></li>
  <p>  What's a new experience without food? Experience Bauchi offers you the opportunity to eat <br>different nutritious foods from the Northern Origin.<br>
    Masa,Suya, Gurasa are awesome foods you should prepare your taste buds for, and more.</p>
    <br>
    <img src="https://9jafoods.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Deliciuos-Masa-Recipe.jpg" alt="Masa Bauchi">

<img src="https://food.jumia.com.ng/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/img_20140216_125432-660x400.jpg" alt="" width ="400px">   </ul>
